    "ratingSource": "Ratings are computed deterministically from a frozen pre-tournament Elo snapshot (elo_baseline.json, fetched 2026-06-11) plus every played result in results.json, applied in date order via the standard World Cup Elo formula (K=60, goal-difference weighted), with each in-tournament result's rating change multiplied by 1.5x (on the basis that current tournament form is more representative of a team's true strength than their pre-tournament rating alone). No live fetch is used, so there is no possibility of double-counting against eloratings.net's own updates. Run scripts/sim/compareToLive.js periodically to check this against live eloratings.net values (noting ours will diverge somewhat by design, due to the multiplier).",
